# cmake macro to test if we use gphoto2
#  GPHOTO2_FOUND - system has the GPHOTO2 library
#  GPHOTO2_INCLUDE_DIR - the GPHOTO2 include directory
#  GPHOTO2_LIBRARIES - The libraries needed to use GPHOTO2

